org.cytoscape.io.internal.cxio

Class CxExporter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cytoscape.io.internal.cxio.CxExporter

  • public class CxExporter
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is for serializing Cytoscape networks, views, and attribute tables as CX formatted output streams.

    In particular, it provides the following methods for writing CX:
    • writeCX(CyNetwork, AspectSet, OutputStream)
    • writeCX(CyNetworkView, AspectSet, OutputStream)
    • writeCX(CyNetwork, AspectSet, FilterSet, OutputStream)
    • writeCX(CyNetworkView, AspectSet, FilterSet, OutputStream)


    These methods use:
    • AspectSet to control which aspects to serialize
    • FilterSet to control which aspect keys/fields to include within an aspect

    See Also:
    AspectSet, Aspect, FilterSet, CxOutput, CxImporter

      • writeCX

        public final CxOutput writeCX(org.cytoscape.model.CyNetwork network,
                              AspectSet aspects,
                              FilterSet filters,
                              java.io.OutputStream out)
                       throws java.io.IOException
        This is a method for serializing a Cytoscape network and associated table data as CX formatted OutputStream.
        Method arguments control which aspects to serialize, and for data stored in node and tables (serialized as node attributes and edge attributes aspects), which table columns to include or exclude.
        Parameters:
        network - the CyNetwork, and by association, tables to be serialized
        aspects - the set of aspects to serialize
        filters - the set of filters controlling which node and edge table columns to include or exclude
        out - the stream to write to
        Returns:
        a CxOutput object which contains the output stream as well as a status
        Throws:
        java.io.IOException
        See Also:
        AspectSet, Aspect, FilterSet, CxOutput
